-- Impregilo Signs Agreement With Shanghai Electric for Desalination Venture
-- B y   D a n   L i e f g r e e n
-- 2010-10-07T11:59:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-07/impregilo-signs-agreement-with-shanghai-electric-for-desalination-venture.html
Impregilo SpA said it signed a letter
of intent for cooperation in the desalination industry with
Shanghai Electric Group Co., Mandarin Capital Partners and China
Development Bank Securities. Impregilo made the announcement in
a stock-exchange statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Liefgreen at 
 dliefgreen@bloomberg.net  